title: Cozy spacious apartment with a view, by UCSF, Golden Gate Park
posting_body: ['Live in a great location and pay low rent!', 'Newly renovated kitchen!!!', ' And newly refinished hardwood floors....', 'A spacious one bedroom and one bathroom apartment on the top floor with a view, includes a kitchenette, a sizable living room, a large bedroom closet, and a large bedroom, bathroom, and kitchen, with laundry facilities on site.', 'Located at Kirkham St and 16th Ave.', 'Right by the, "Hidden Garden Steps."', 'The apartment is also walking distance to food delivery services, restaurants, take-out, and fast food places.', 'Nearby are the MUNI bus stop #6 and the underground MUNI N light rail which can bring you downtown in approximately 15-20 minutes.', 'To schedule a tour, please contact/text Josephine:  415-2O5-7347']
